      • addColumnMetadata

        public void addColumnMetadata(ColumnDef cdef)
                       throws javax.jdo.JDOException,
                              javax.jdo.JDOUserException,
                              NullPointerException

        Add a column to this TypeDef.

        Parameters:
        cdef - ColumnDef
        Throws:
        javax.jdo.JDOException - if the column position in the given ColumnDef does not match the next available column position at this TypeDef.
        javax.jdo.JDOUserException - if this is unmodifiable or another column with the same name is already present at this TypeDef.
        NullPointerException - if ColumnDef is null
